  "description": [
    "THE NOME NUGGET Published Monday Wednesday and Friday by the NOME PUBLISHING CO Nome Alaska Telephone 4432381 Si30 Per Month PO Box 66 1600 a Year James F OSullivan Publisher Editor Ed Jocius Foreman Entered at second class matter October 14 1943 at the post office at Nome Alaska under Act of March 3 1879 A S3 tV AT WATCH IT ANDREI REMEMBER PINNOCHIO The Role of Profit in American Life The role of profit in American life is frequently even com monly misunderstood A good many people regard it as an unfair charge against the consumers of goods and services an imposed tithe in effect by which the few benefit at the expense of the many The fact is that if it werent for profit the many as well as the few would find themselves in a sorry condition indeed For it is profit fairly earned that keeps the economy of this country running precisely as gasoline runs your car R G Follis Chairman of the Board of the Standard Oil Company of California tells the story well in these words By any name and it has been given many profit is a margin of economic growth It is"
